-- 3. "Las celdas" вҶ’ "The cells" but original said "Cells" (no article)
-- 4. "bajo presiГіn de oracle" вҶ’ "under oracle pressure" вҖ” this one survives.
-- 5. "Cell es el Scheme de los LLMs" вҶ’ "Cell is the Scheme of LLMs" вҖ” survives.

