-- вҠўвҲҳ refine used 2 of 5 allowed iterations.
-- Self-correction: iteration 0 found and fixed 2 semantic drifts.
-- Iteration 1 confirmed the fixes held through the round-trip.

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- OBSERVATIONS
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў= obs-back-translation-as-verification
  given В§21-self-correcting-translator
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "BACK-TRANSLATION IS A SEMANTIC DIFF ORACLE: The program uses no reference translation вҖ” it verifies quality by translating BACK to English and comparing against the original. This is proof-carrying computation applied to NL: the back-translation is the certificate, the diff cell is the verifier. The verifier (diff) is easier than the task (translate) вҖ” comparing two English texts for semantic equivalence is simpler than producing a correct Spanish translation. This is the P-vs-NP asymmetry Cell exploits: generate in NP space, verify in P space."

вҠў= obs-guard-clauses-replace-conditional-body
  given В§21-self-correcting-translator
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "GUARD CLAUSES SPLIT R16's MONOLITHIC correct CELL: R16 had one correct cell with 'if acceptable then output unchanged, else retranslate.' v0.2 splits this into two guard-gated cells: correct (where acceptable=false) does retranslation, accept-unchanged (where acceptable=true) passes through unchanged. Only one fires per iteration. accept-unchanged is вҠў= (deterministic вҖ” just copies the input), while correct is вҲҙ (soft вҖ” needs LLM for retranslation). Guard clauses reveal that the 'pass-through' case never needed an LLM at all. R16 wasted an LLM call on 'output unchanged' вҖ” v0.2 eliminates this."

вҠў= obs-aspirational-oracles-in-loop
  given В§21-self-correcting-translator
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "вҠўвҲҳ-MANAGED ORACLES ARE ASPIRATIONAL, NOT GATES: translate's oracles (Spanish-only, same sentence count, metacircular present) all PASS in this trace, but under v0.2 they would not block freezing even if they failed. The вҠўвҲҳ until condition (diffвҶ’acceptable = true) is the real gate. This matters for robustness: if translate's 'same sentence count' oracle failed (LLM merged two sentences), the loop would still iterate and diff would catch it. The aspirational oracles provide diagnostic information вҖ” their failure messages would appear in the through chain context вҖ” but they don't independently veto."

вҠў= obs-conditional-oracle-vacuous-satisfaction
  given В§21-self-correcting-translator
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "CONDITIONAL ORACLE VACUOUS SATISFACTION IS LOAD-BEARING: diff has 4 oracles, 3 of which are conditional. In iteration 0 (drift-score=3): 'if drift-score=0 then segments empty' is vacuously satisfied (falseвҶ’P is true). In iteration 1 (drift-score=1): 'if drift-score>1 then acceptable=false' is vacuously satisfied. Without the v0.2 vacuous-satisfaction rule, these oracles would be ambiguous вҖ” does a false precondition mean skip or fail? The spec's choice (standard logic: falseвҶ’P is true) means conditional oracles never produce false negatives from irrelevant conditions."

вҠў= obs-convergence-in-two-iterations
  given В§21-self-correcting-translator
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "TWO ITERATIONS IS REALISTIC FOR TRANSLATION CORRECTION: Iteration 0 found 2 drifted segments (self-bootstrappingвҶ’auto-bootstrapping, fills inвҶ’completes). The correct cell retranslated only those segments. Iteration 1 confirmed the fixes held: drift-score dropped from 3 to 1. The residual drift-score=1 reflects minor stylistic differences (startвҶ’begin, article variations) that don't affect implementor meaning. The вҠўвҲҳ loop's tolerance (drift-score вүӨ 1 is acceptable) prevents infinite polishing of irrelevant stylistic differences. This is the right convergence criterion: semantic fidelity, not surface-form identity."

вҠў= obs-file-scope-recovery-as-safety-net
  given В§21-self-correcting-translator
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "FILE-SCOPE вҠЁ? PROVIDES DEFENSE IN DEPTH: The file-scope recovery policy (retry max 3, exhaustion вҶ’ error-value(вҠҘ)) applies to any cell without its own вҠЁ?. In this trace no cell's oracles fail outside the вҠўвҲҳ loop, so the file-scope policy is never activated. But if diff's oracles failed (e.g., drift-score was outside 0-10), the file-scope вҠЁ? would retry diff up to 3 times before yielding вҠҘ for all diff outputs. This would propagate вҠҘ to both correct and accept-unchanged (blocking both via their given deps), effectively halting the вҠўвҲҳ loop. R16 had per-cell вҠЁ? only on correct вҖ” v0.2 file-scope вҠЁ? covers ALL cells uniformly."

вҠў= obs-accept-unchanged-crystallization
  given В§21-self-correcting-translator
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "accept-unchanged IS A CRYSTALLIZATION DISCOVERY: R16's correct cell handled both branches (pass-through and retranslation) in one вҲҙ body. Splitting via guard clauses revealed that the pass-through branch is FULLY DETERMINISTIC вҖ” it just copies translateвҶ’spanish-text. In v0.2 it becomes вҠў= (hard cell), needing no LLM at all. This is crystallization-by-refactoring: the act of applying v0.2 guard clauses exposed a latent deterministic computation hiding inside a soft cell. The retranslation branch (correct) remains soft вҖ” it genuinely needs LLM judgment to retranslate drifted segments."
